'This Program Gives an Example of Sending 
'Voltage, Current, Temperature, and Position data to a 4x20 LCD Display.
'This is good for setting up limits on torque down applications
'This assumes you have an Animatics 4x20 Anilink Display wired to a motor

'The followin gline of code initises the LCD display, clears it
' and places the curser at the upper left hand corner.

PRINT(#56,#12,#6,#1)	'SETUP OF LCD

'GOSUB0		'Initialise text on the display
GOSUB1		'Go to LCD update subroutine

END


'C0
' PRINT(#128,"  Volts :           ")
